      "rationale": "Experimental test conditions documented to match CFD boundary conditions: inlet flow rates (2–6 L/min), rotational speeds (2000–3500 RPM), fluid temperature (37°C ± 0.5°C), and blood analog viscosity (0.0035 Pa·s). Measurement uncertainty on flow rate ±1.5%, on pressure ±0.5 mmHg. All five operating points replicated in both experiment and simulation. Achieved Gradation 2 meets MRL 2 requirement."
    },
