      "rationale": "Quantitative comparison metrics applied: normalized root-mean-square error (NRMSE) for velocity fields (NRMSE = 4.1%), relative error on RH index across all 5 operating points (max 6.8%), and pressure head agreement within 3.2%. Statistical validation metric (Oberkampf-Trucano) computed with U_val = 0.07. All comparison metrics satisfy acceptance thresholds. Achieved Gradation 3 exceeds MRL 2 requirement of Gradation 2."
