      "rationale": "Iterative convergence monitored via residual norms; all continuity and momentum residuals reduced to below 1e-5 before solution acceptance. Mass imbalance across pump domain confirmed below 0.01%. Round-off error assessed negligible at double-precision arithmetic. Solver error contribution bounded and documented in solver QA log SQA-2023-03. Achieved Gradation 1 meets MRL 2 requirement of Gradation 1."
    },
