      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "https://uofa.net/morrison/criteria/use-error-mrl2-acceptance",
      "rationale": "Simulation setup checklist completed and independently reviewed. Boundary condition assignments verified against COU specification document. Turbulence model selection (SST k-omega) justified and documented. Independent analyst reproduced key results confirming no setup errors. Use error controls documented in simulation execution plan SEP-2023-01. Achieved Gradation 1 meets MRL 2 requirement."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
