      "acceptanceCriteria": "https://uofa.net/morrison/criteria/model-form-mrl2-acceptance",
      "rationale": "Reynolds-averaged Navier-Stokes (RANS) with SST k-omega turbulence closure selected based on published benchmark studies for rotating blood pump flows. Power-law hemolysis damage model (Giersiepen-Wurzinger) applied with literature-validated coefficients. Model form assumptions documented and justified in model description document MDD-2023-02. Sensitivity of hemolysis prediction to turbulence model assessed via comparison with k-epsilon results (difference < 8%). Achieved Gradation 2 exceeds MRL 2 requirement of Gradation 1."
    },
