      "rationale": "All model input parameters sourced from traceable references: blood analog viscosity from rheometry measurements (report RHE-2022-04), pump geometry from CAD drawings with CMM verification, rotational speed from tachometer calibration records. Input uncertainty ranges quantified and propagated through one-at-a-time sensitivity analysis. Input parameter traceability matrix documented in IPT-2023-01. Achieved Gradation 2 meets MRL 2 requirement."
