      "rationale": "Experimental measurements obtained from three replicate test runs per operating point (n=3 per condition, 15 total runs). Repeatability assessed; coefficient of variation on RH index below 4% across replicates. Test sample documentation includes fluid batch records, temperature logs, and instrument calibration certificates. Sample adequacy justified relative to MRL 2 requirements. Achieved Gradation 1 meets MRL 2 requirement."
